Dwayne Harvard and Steven Sutton got into an argument Sunday night in Springdale, Pennsylvania . 
  Harvard was giving Sutton's girlfriend a ride home . 
  The two men argued over the fact that he was giving her a ride . 
  Harvard drove through seven towns with Sutton on the hood of his car . 
  He has been charged with aggravated assault, reckless endangerment and DUI . 
  Harvard claims he was not the one who attacked him . 
 